==Series 2==
Unlike the first series, the feature car of each episode was shown being sold at auction at the [[National Exhibition Centre|NEC]], Birmingham, at the end of the episode (instead of being sold at the end of the series). Starting from episode 2 onward, Ant is given the car for £0 by the owner to restore the car back to its original state; any money that is made at the auction is given to the owner.

