==Broadcast==
In [[Australia]], Series 1 first aired in 2014 on [[ABC (Australian TV channel)|ABC]].<ref name=ABC-2014>{{cite web|title=For The Love of Cars : ABC TV|url=http://www.abc.net.au/tv/programs/for-the-love-of-cars/|website=[[ABC (Australian TV channel)|ABC]]|publisher=[[Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]|accessdate=7 December 2015}}</ref> Series 1 also aired on [[subscription television]] channel [[Discovery Turbo]], beginning on 17 July 2015.<ref name="July10Fox">{{cite web|publisher=The Green Room|url=http://community.foxtel.com.au/t5/Foxtel-Blog/Ray-Donovan-The-Firm-The-Strain-Safe-House-and-live-sport/ba-p/81811|title=Ray Donovan, The Firm, The Strain, Safe House and live sport|date=10 July 2015|accessdate=15 July 2015}}</ref> Series 2 premiered on [[9Go!]] on 1 December 2015.<ref name=9Go!-2015>{{cite web|title=Watch For The Love of Cars|url=http://www.9jumpin.com.au/show/fortheloveofcars/episodes/|website=9Jumpin|publisher=[[Nine Entertainment Co]]|accessdate=7 December 2015}}</ref>

